dc_title_s: Estate map of Thomas P. Cook on Manasquan River
dc_description_s: This is an incomplete section of a map that shows property along the Manasquan River. Among the property lots delineated include the Thomas Cook estate, the Captain Henry Green Estate, Captain James T. Longstreet estate, Hendrick Voorhees, and widow John Longstreet properties. Several roads, bridges, and property improvements are also depicted. The map is a tracing in poor condition.|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
